POWERCOM CO LTD (3043)  said unconsolidated sales
in December fell 81.89% to NT$96,997,000 from NT$535,500,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  12/2011          12/2010
Sales             96,997          535,500    
YOY%             -81.89%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           3,811,930        6,246,007   
YOY%             -38.97% 
=================================================================
 